text: Diána Csányi (born 20 March 1998) is a Hungarian footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Hungary women's national team. ==Career== Csányi has been capped for the Hungary national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian women's footballers Category:Hungary women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders
